{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because Holland, like Britain, had a big empire, actually, which not many people seem to understand or know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had lots of possessions in both East Indies and the West Indies-- the West Indies, Java, Sumatra, and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's all now Indonesia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That all belonged to Holland before the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So our lessons in geography, et cetera, included all those kind of countries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was all part of Holland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the same, the Dutch West Indies-- sorry, the other one is the East Indies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In West Indies, in Guyana, Curacao, and Suriname, for example, that was all part of Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, and this boy, Carmelo, he came from Suriname or Curacao, one, one of those.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was brown, black.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, and he was the only one in the whole school, and then one of the few, actually, [LAUGHS] in Holland or Heemstede.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In that area, everybody knew him kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I think he stood out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But nobody was bothered about him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he was one of my best friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Those two were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Strangely enough, Carmelo still lives in the same house that he lived in-- [LAUGHTER] --in those days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's how I found him, kind of-- 13 [NON-ENGLISH] in Haarlem, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And after 60 years, he's still in the same house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he still looks the same-- brown.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And yes, it was good, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Unfortunately-- well, another good thing was our father often took us to restaurants in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He-- because he worked in Amsterdam, he went by tram every day from Heemstede to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He knew Amsterdam pretty well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we particularly developed a taste for various restaurants in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
